library(mice)
imp = mice(nhanes, m=5, printFlag=FALSE, maxit = 40, seed=2525)
library(mi)
fit.mi = with(data=imp, exp = lm(chl ~ age + bmi))
combFit = mice::pool(fit.mi)
summary(combFit)
